## ğŸ”§ Development

### Setup
```bash
# Clone and install
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ReadmeGen.git
cd ReadmeGen
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e .[dev]
```

### Testing
```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=readme_generator
```

